ss=\"lucide lucide-chevron-left\"><path d=\"m15 18-6-6 6-6\"></path></svg> Voltar</a><div class=\"text-center mb-8\"><span class=\"badge bg-green-100 text-green-700 text-sm mb-3\">Assinatura Mensal</span><h1 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900\">Ative seu perfil de prestador</h1><p class=\"text-gray-500 mt-2\">Pague via PIX e comece a receber pedidos na sua região.</p></div><div class=\"card p-6 mb-6 border-2 border-primary-200 bg-primary-50\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div><p class=\"font-bold text-lg text-gray-900\">Plano Prestador</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mt-0.5\">Acesso completo à plataforma ABCResolve</p></div><div class=\"text-right\"><p class=\"text-3xl font-extrabold text-primary-700\">R$ 19<span class=\"text-xl\">,90</span></p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400\">por mês</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-4 grid grid-cols-2 gap-2\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-1.5 text-sm text-gray-700\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check-big text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\"><path d=\"M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg>Perfil verificado visível aos clientes</div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-1.5 text-sm text-gray-700\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check-big text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\"><path d=\"M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg>Receba pedidos ilimitados</div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-1.5 text-sm text-gray-700\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check-big text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\"><path d=\"M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg>Destaque na sua categoria</div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-1.5 text-sm text-gray-700\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check-big text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\"><path d=\"M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg>Suporte por e-mail</div></div></div><div class=\"card p-6 text-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-5\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-smartphone text-green-600\"><rect width=\"14\" height=\"20\" x=\"5\" y=\"2\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900\">Pague com PIX</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center py-16\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-loader-circle animate-spin text-primary-500\"><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-6.219-8.56\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"mt-5 pt-5 border-t border-gray-100 space-y-2\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\"